-- Serena Williams Defeats Defending Champion Kvitova at Wimbledon
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2012-07-03T15:24:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-03/serena-williams-defeats-defending-champion-kvitova-at-wimbledon.html
Four-time singles champion  Serena
Williams  defeated Wimbledon title holder Petra Kvitova to
advance to the semifinals of the grass court tennis tournament.  Williams won 6-3, 7-5 under the roof on Centre Court. Play
on outside courts has been suspended because of rain in London.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Christopher Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  